also , i would hardly dare sell this house to anybody now that the creatures have taken notice of it .
they seem to be trying to get the black stone back and destroy the phonograph record , but i shall not let them if i can help it .
my great police dogs always hold them back , for there are very few here as yet , and they are clumsy in getting about .
as i have said , their wings are not much use for short flights on earth .
